docs.lead_paragraph: The second cabin passengers of the Guion Line steamship Wyoming, who have been held in quarantine since Sept. 6, have issued the following appeals to the public:

headline.main: WYOMING PASSENGERS APPEAL.; THEY ASK TO BE SET FREE FROM A SHIP WHICH IS NOT INFECTED.
